_sText: In the meantime i fixing up the zm_toxic, i made this map. I tried to make it stylish and looking different from other zombie mod maps. It is only alpha, dont forget. I tried to balance spots aswell, so ppl dont whine about it. map has two secret teleporters, one secret label, and secret music. I paked all custom files into the bsp, report any misses please. Have fun.
